<span id="freeTextContainer6748569804560678867">Nice mystery. Exciting. Good sense of place and time (important in an historical.) Believable characters. I&apos;m waiting for the promised Maledictus.<br/><br/>My only quibble would be that although Ms Stanley is a classicist, most of her readers are not. It would have been nice to have had contextual clues to the many Latin words. There is a glossary but flipping to the back takes me out of the story.</span>
